<div><h3>GAME 175 - Writing for Fantasy & RPGs </h3>  <hr>This course covers the broad palette of fantasy and its sub-genres, genre- and lore-appropriate game-text, character development within fantasy, world development within fantasy, writing within the constraints of game development tools, traditional narrative storytelling, cinematic scripts, voiceover scripts, dialogue and narrative, writing specs, writing proposals, writing for established intellectual properties, and analysis of existing games.<br><br><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> GAME 075<br><br><strong>Anticipated Terms Offered:</strong> Spring<br><br></div>		</td>
